{"tid":618133,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"裕美失守 猴擒男友狂攻下身","createTime":"2018-04-05T14:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T16:01:37.000Z","uid":136588,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c86968c8709e18982e37c6fe33e0b8be4a0a2d0b","tid":618133,"uid":136588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"日前裕美着住條超短褲，跟老外男朋友Alex出外吃飯，她跟Alex擁作一團，躺餐廳長櫈上，當其他食客冇到。Alex入直路，摸女友大髀摸得好梳乎，手臂更貼實女友下身，裕美亦胸壓他，派福利！ <br />\n<br />\n戲肉嚟喇，之後Alex向裕美的大髀罅進發，堅係搣落去。之後成隻手攝落去，唔係怕凍啩？Alex當眾探手在她的大腿內側，實在「探索」得太過份，好曳曳呀！失守的裕美終於推開他，話晒大庭廣眾，太猴擒喇！ <br />\n<br />\n兩個咀完又咀，埋單之後Alex努力「撻着」裕美，在街上暗角都咀唔停。最後傾掂數，齊齊打的返歸，相信愈夜愈精彩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GArlXB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GArlXB&d=0Caqpc71t%2FLvHRJho41rpwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cf156870\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GArlXB</a>"},{"pid":"ed0799331457ee5851909923846886cc35e88eb1","tid":618133,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"七天中的希冀 我屌你老味～"},{"pid":"7013a9574668a150a53055cbc794c064e8ec96e7","tid":618133,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"有冇之前脫褲既圖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf7cd312717cc65ef3eaf1ac1cd11dcfdbd450a","tid":618133,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:26:07.000Z","msg":"好耐未聽過裕美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f63484336716531ee2726e723d2d383edcf248c","tid":618133,"uid":142432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T16:01:37.000Z","msg":"蘋果唔係霉到要跟暗星啊話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}